data.description: Seller offering a $10,000 concession towards closing costs, buy down, or down payment assistance!!!  Over $40,000 in upgrades in the past year! Welcome to this charming ranch home in Prairie Greens with mountain views! Enjoy the convenience of one level living with open floor plan and natural light. Step inside the lovely living room with vaulted ceilings that leads you to the spacious eat in kitchen. Kitchen flows to back patio that overlooks the white picket fenced yard complete with the gorgeous back range mountain views. This home offers three spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space and 2 baths. Laundry room with washer/dryer included. Many updates including- New flooring throughout, New window coverings, New high impact roof, and New A/C. This home is completed with an attached 2 car garage. Prairie Green is a charming land lease community with pool, park, fitness center and clubhouse. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely home your own.
